Game Modes:
- Quick:
    - Duel - fight another wizard
    - Hunt - Kill magic monsters / beasts
- Long:
    - Battle/Survive - Hold off hordes of enemies 
    - Tournament - standard roguelike - fight you way through duels as you acquire boosts



